{"word":"στωμύλλω","slug":"στωμύλλω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στωμύλλω</b></el> <el>(στωμύλλω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:στωμύλος'><el>στωμύλος</el></a>, as <a href='S:στρογγύλλω'><el>στρογγύλλω</el></a> from <a href='S:στρογγύλος'><el>στρογγύλος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to be talkative, to chatter, babble</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—so as <a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <el>στωμύλλομαι</el>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>στωμυλοῦμαι</el>, aor1 <el>ἐστωμυλάμην</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}